data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite single-family residence nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood. This luxurious 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home boasts elegance and comfort throughout. The spacious floor plan creates an exceptional indoor and outdoor living experience.

Step inside and be greeted by the stunning interior, and an abundance of natural light. The living room is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy evenings by the fireplace. The kitchen is equipped with SS appliances, sleek granite countertops, and ample storage space for a chef's dream.

Retreat to the master suite, complete with lavish bathroom, individual bath tub, walk-in shower, private water closet, and large walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms offer versatility and comfort for family members or guests. 

Enjoy the expansive backyard, screened porch, fire pit, and elevated brick patio. All surrounded by a private fence.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning residence your home.
